properties.areaDesc: Los Angeles County Coast including Downtown Los Angeles
properties.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued January 24 at 11:08PM PST until January 25 at 8:00AM PST by NWS Los Angeles/Oxnard CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Visibility one quarter mile or less in dense fog.

* WHERE...Los Angeles County Coast including Downtown Los
Angeles.

* WHEN...Until 8 AM PST Saturday.

* IMPACTS...Very low visibility will create dangerous driving
conditions.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Fog will affect travel on most area
roadways including Pacific Coast Highway and the 10, 105, 110,
405, 605, and 710 freeways.
properties.instruction:
If driving, slow down, use your headlights, and leave plenty of
distance ahead of you.

NWSheadline: DENSE FOG ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 8 AM PST SATURDAY
